Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.760
Hello!

00:00:01.220 --> 00:00:04.690
There are going to be a lot of holidays in May, so prepare for a lot of Specials!

00:00:04.690 --> 00:00:06.530
But first things first.

00:00:06.890 --> 00:00:11.800
From the 1st to the 6th of May, there will be a Special dedicated to John Walter Christie's birthday.

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:15.580
That means you'll have discounts for some light and medium tanks,

00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:20.730
and some missions that will bring you equipment and extra crew experience.

00:00:21.230 --> 00:00:25.710
Starting from the 1st to the 8th of May, there will be a “Discount for the Day” offer,

00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:30.350
so if you are dreaming about some premium tank,

00:00:30.490 --> 00:00:34.670
watch for the discounts and buy it 30% percent cheaper.

00:00:35.020 --> 00:00:39.200
Before the 18th of May, you can convert your Free experience to Crew experience.

00:00:39.530 --> 00:00:44.460
Get that light bulb for every commander who doesn't have it yet!

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:48.750
The Victory Day Special will take its place from 8th to 11th of May.

00:00:49.080 --> 00:00:53.200
I'll tell about it more in another video. So don't miss the news!

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:58.160
In May, our shop will offer you a special “Berlin Triplet” package,

00:00:58.160 --> 00:01:04.570
that is, three unique Soviet tanks: the IS-2, the ISU-122S and the Т-34-85 “Rudy”.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.360
Yep, that Rudy!

00:01:06.620 --> 00:01:10.460
And rumors have it that in its crew, there's even a four-legged companion!

00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:15.900
From the 22nd to the 25th of May, there will be a historic Special,

00:01:16.110 --> 00:01:20.350
“Fast tank”, dedicated to first FT at their combat alert duty.

00:01:20.570 --> 00:01:25.260
In the game, you'll get discounts for some light and medium tanks,

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:28.300
premium vehicles of Tiers VI and VII,

00:01:28.300 --> 00:01:32.120
and also discounts for skill reset, crew training and retraining.

00:01:32.650 --> 00:01:36.960
For completing missions you can get extra crew experience and extra equipment.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:40.650
Asya's traditional discounts are here, too!

00:01:40.830 --> 00:01:43.680
What are they? Let's see!

00:01:52.060 --> 00:01:54.000
Hello players! The April is almost over,

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:57.630
and it's time to find out what discounts will bring you joy in May.

00:01:57.630 --> 00:01:59.950
Let our lottery drum help us!

00:02:08.510 --> 00:02:12.040
The first one is the Object 268.

00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:17.710
All branch of this tank will have discounts

00:02:17.710 --> 00:02:19.390
and bonuses for training the crew.

00:02:20.430 --> 00:02:23.660
Let's find out who's the another lucky duck!

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:28.940
Spin it!

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:33.690
Well…

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:36.640
It's the M46 Patton.

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:43.870
Its branch will have the discounts and bonuses as well.

00:02:45.160 --> 00:02:48.120
You can find out the details of the Special in the game.

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:50.010
Good luck!

00:02:50.490 --> 00:02:51.930
